1025
01:51:34,214 --> 01:51:38,062
Hej, nenechávaj ma tu samu.

1026
01:51:42,252 --> 01:51:43,180
Morris.

1027
01:52:58,057 --> 01:53:01,091
Tak dlho som na teba čakala.

1028
01:53:02,019 --> 01:53:05,548
